{"tid":1128544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打們對上一次夢遺係幾時呢～～～","createTime":"2019-04-28T01:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T09:58:10.000Z","uid":243838,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b14ea8d5f9b8e67ac35e36b6b5c59a892b5c5c","tid":1128544,"uid":243838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:14:30.000Z","msg":"如題～～～<br />\n我覺得而家啲男仔應該冇夢遺呢樣野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我有個諗法，可以自己製作夢遺嗎？<br />\n<br />\n首先我有以下區分先（純粹個人見解）：<br />\n做愛享受度：靈魂100% 肉體100%<br />\n打丁享受度：靈魂50%   肉體50%<br />\n夢遺享受度：靈魂100% 肉體75%<br />\n因此當冇得做愛時夢遺係最好嘅代替方式～<br />\n<br />\n但發生夢遺嘅或然率好低～因爲要有好多野配合！<br />\n大家有冇好似我咁無聊試諗過點樣令呢個機率提升呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83902679982da0dcc0fcf37082dc9522df7b22f","tid":1128544,"uid":224570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:18:50.000Z","msg":"樓主死毒撚返去打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757831f50195a6ee2857ef893029c7d6eee28ae8","tid":1128544,"uid":225950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085d5ab54f2df40a16cc242e951dea10600e4857","tid":1128544,"uid":27064,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:22:12.000Z","msg":"爽係好爽 但要起身洗底褲好煩<br />\n最慘有時連被、床褥都濕埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840785b388505276f2f1b9aead1a9765768e187a","tid":1128544,"uid":33497,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:23:38.000Z","msg":"一次夢遺都未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120004b2b4d6724d83e4b68031377960ecf11301","tid":1128544,"uid":133505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"唔打丁一個月就會夢遺到，好似係"},{"pid":"5da075fec3da9deda5b5d027dff877f09cd5ed30","tid":1128544,"uid":205844